Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位 决战的时刻终于到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时至今日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与维甘的战斗已成为你我生活中的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从父母到孩子 世世代代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无一例外的经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在维甘恐怖威胁下 煎熬的日日夜夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们今天之所以站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为我们 不畏流血牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不放弃 直至最后的战斗精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来到这里的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们除将胜利纳入囊中没有第二种选择
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘要塞拉·格拉密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.58,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为维甘侵略地球的据点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是摧毁我军前总司令部 巨环基地的罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我军蒙受过重大损失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们将报一箭之仇 攻略拉·格拉密斯要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护地球免于维甘的蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以一场毋庸置疑的胜利 为战争画下休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝诸位武运昌隆！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳图尔舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各部门 按作战命令书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达新模式的测试听说已经完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出击前去听一下说明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳图尔舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇少校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗在即啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会是一场硬仗 全靠上校了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然变得好严肃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子戴得紧 是紧张的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿戴得这么严实 是焦虑的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都被你看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,率领队伍 自然而然养成了观察周围的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我连自己的事都顾不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决战近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却好像完全没有成长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有自己的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是第一次面临这样大规模的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对严峻的形势
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能声称自己准备万全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为了完成自己的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不安也只能前行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是… 我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳图尔·艾纳斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有你的指挥风格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:06:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:06:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要决战了 吉欧也很忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不情愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了即将出现的伤员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备这些药品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我说的话 最好是用不到它们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧上战场我是不会拦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为吉欧并不是去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会用我的方式结束战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要平安回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才来 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-FX的新模式调试已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫FX 爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FX 爆发模式？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FX 爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把AGE-FX的机动力提高到最大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会对射击精准度造成略微影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要活用这种模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以实现单机的大量杀敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只须从驾驶舱里执行程序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AGE-FX就可以变身为FX爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看你怎么用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不明白的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 出击前有话想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你停止那种想拯救敌人的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种战斗方式 牺牲的是你自己的安全！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该保护的不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是自己 是战友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此不得不干掉敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人也不会对你手软
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决战的日子终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗 是我们维甘走向未来的唯一道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论什么困难 都无法阻止我们的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法阻止我们得到新的未来 得到伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是伊泽尔坎特大人为我们铺设的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理想之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.74,0:10:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊甸在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}伊甸在我手中 伊甸在我手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨那伦多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要全力辅佐杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经将伊甸计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全权托付给杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信杰哈特能够带领大家走上正确的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要成为杰哈特的左膀右臂助他实现计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本应该由你成为我的继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你能继承我的DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却无法继承我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂已经由杰哈特继承
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你则作为最强的机师辅佐杰哈特左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住吗 泽拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向联邦军全体将士通话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们即将开始进攻敌人要塞 拉·格拉密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准放过一个维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员 战斗态势
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 我看你的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不想用FX爆发模式？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是敌人也不愿意去滥加屠杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不杀敌人 敌人就会杀你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发了 大家准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.27,0:12:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别急着放弃 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们一定会理解你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.77,0:12:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用我的方法结束这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 阿比斯队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥布莱特·洛伦 杰诺亚斯O特装型 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔纳森·斯塔姆 克兰修出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德雷克·嘉克罗 克兰修出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍利奇·阿比斯 克兰修特装型出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧·明日野 高达AGE-FX出击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆 你想像过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当自己站在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们建立的伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中只有那里的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无法抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都将归于无
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂 杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必将抵达伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便以我的生命交换 也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我重要的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部下…这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最需要防备的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一击摧毁巨环基地的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人要塞的高能量密度巨炮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在的射线轴上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍有维甘舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下 不至于会发射吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉·格拉密斯要塞炮 迪格玛泽隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方一定认为它现在无用武之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种异样感是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 为什么不朝我开炮？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德雷克 你想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘战舰有问题 说不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要单独行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 德雷克机？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德雷克中尉正单独靠近B350的敌舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是 该舰的舰炮射击有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央的敌人舰队是假像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令全军散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪格玛泽隆炮 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战舰法拉第 斯泰鲁斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北卡 埃利奥特 失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机动战士队 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦格雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各部队 敌人要塞炮为充填能量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下次发射前有一定间隔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁此机会 在敌人防守薄弱的射线轴上寻找机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央突破！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号带队突前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动用等离子爆破炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向拉·格拉密斯实施打击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 纳图尔舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号 最大战速
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 我们也正面突破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么轻易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是伊泽尔坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被攻击这里也在意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先结果你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 芙拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:19:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动FX 爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 以一敌二也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会去用FX爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了保护人们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想做那些夺人性命的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我的 用FX爆发模式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的援军？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,误射？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…不是什么误射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨那伦多的部队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.41,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是你们的坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特大人 您快走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能应付吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二波攻击队 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着这一刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天要为他们报仇雪恨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊… 这台机体还在调试中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.99,0:21:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么吃的 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不能出击还要它干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.19,0:21:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台可以用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格尔多林吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄恩·亚农 吉尔斯拜因出击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈德·戴拿姆 格尔多林出击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉欧 你也在这个战场上吗？
